  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine behavioral and functional brain changes occuring as
      a result of cognitive remediation training in patients with schizophrenia. Extension and
      specificity of related changes will also be examined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
